{"tid":2333152,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"myprotein點解可以咁撚難飲","createTime":"2020-12-20T07:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T17:55:58.000Z","uid":121289,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2bfbd052a2d9deb9471a32b3992d6baeacb642da","tid":2333152,"uid":121289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T07:32:18.000Z","msg":"之前買過myprotein隻clear isolate<br />\n飲落覺得麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩除左mojito之外其他都叫飲得下落口<br />\n今次諗住買正常d口味 買左奶茶 朱古力 strawberry cream各2.5kg<br />\n一飲落去真係屌你老味 3隻味都中撚哂伏<br />\n代糖味仲重過之前果D clear isolate<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朱古力同strawberry頭果陣味都叫接受到 但飲第2啖就覺得難飲到仆街<br />\n奶茶就直頭垃圾 第一啖都衰過人 仲衰過一般超市買果D即沖奶茶好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底班英國佬賣之前有冇自己試飲過先 咁離譜個味道都拎黎賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢送D零食我又覺得幾OK 反而呢個仲覺得買得過<br />\n但係d粉就真係離哂大譜 寧願食多d雞胸都唔想再飲落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有3包2.5kg宜家都唔知點頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ecafce213bd266cd01cd11069afb987cf37e815","tid":2333152,"uid":224741,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"2bfbd052a2d9deb9471a32b3992d6baeacb642da","tid":2333152,"uid":121289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T07:32:18.000Z","msg":"之前買過myprotein隻clear isolate<br />\n飲落覺得麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩除左mojito之外其他都叫飲得下落口<br />\n今次諗住買正常d口味 買左奶茶 朱古力 strawberry cream各2.5kg<br />\n一飲落去真係屌你老味 3隻味都中撚哂伏<br />\n代糖味仲重過之前果D clear isolate<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朱古力同strawberry頭果陣味都叫接受到 但飲第2啖就覺得難飲到仆街<br />\n奶茶就直頭垃圾 第一啖都衰過人 仲衰過一般超市買果D即沖奶茶好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底班英國佬賣之前有冇自己試飲過先 咁離譜個味道都拎黎賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢送D零食我又覺得幾OK 反而呢個仲覺得買得過<br />\n但係d粉就真係離哂大譜 寧願食多d雞胸都唔想再飲落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有3包2.5kg宜家都唔知點頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T07:40:09.000Z","msg":"同感，但啲人話ok唔知咩口味來，我覺得雲來拿唔似得來幾好飲"},{"pid":"c3c132baf53063cfebba772bec971dca1fcf33ad","tid":2333152,"uid":227275,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T07:45:08.000Z","msg":"答案係!! 陳國邦 (李斯) <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JJebjw3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJJebjw3.jpg&h=a0ee34e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2Laz5t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2Laz5t.jpg&h=b15df2e2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n因為你都識講係protein點會好飲 啫係silly 癡線 冇可能會發生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSilly發音就係 see Li 斯李<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我地華人社會 習慣將last name 擺前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以!!!!!!! 答案就係李斯喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而做過李斯嘅TVB藝員就係得陳國邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以!!!!!!!!!!!!!答案係!!!!!!!!!陳國邦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VB5YJY3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVB5YJY3.jpg&h=84f4867c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n輕鬆 謝謝大家"},{"pid":"fc0a2b211c716d8b5b6033f6d21b72cbd35d1a43","tid":2333152,"uid":12447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T08:03:37.000Z","msg":"佢d朱古力味好伏  士多啤梨就似藥水 <br />\n做咩咁睇唔開一買就2.5kg 明明有sample size試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推薦北海道牛奶 綠茶 Earl grey 最重要係用豆漿或者奶沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4b5c7cdfb5a0389869